{{italic title}}
'''''University of the Air''''' was an educational radio programme produced by the [[Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]] from the late 1950s until 1965, consisting of recorded lectures on various subjects.

In 1965, both this programme and another CBC radio programme, ''[[The Learning Stage]]'', were replaced in favour of a new show, ''[[Ideas (radio show)|Ideas]]'', which is still broadcast on [[CBC Radio One]].

